1
00:00:02,020 --> 00:00:04,940
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="25">This is a world where things like killing 
and torture have been legalized.</font></b></font></font>

2
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:16,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

3
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:18,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You there.</font>

4
00:00:20,440 --> 00:00:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wouldn't happen to be 
interested in torture, would you?</font>

5
00:00:25,060 --> 00:00:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, this?</font>

6
00:00:26,870 --> 00:00:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's fine! It happens all the time!</font>

7
00:00:31,740 --> 00:00:34,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's up with this creep?</i></font>

8
00:00:37,230 --> 00:00:39,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you'd be quite suited to it.</font>

9
00:00:40,110 --> 00:00:41,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

10
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about some torture?</font>

11
00:00:54,330 --> 00:00:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a high school student, right?</font>

12
00:00:57,070 --> 00:00:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a freelance torturer.</font>

13
00:00:59,540 --> 00:01:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you think I'd be right for torture?</font>

14
00:01:04,740 --> 00:01:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you have an overabundance 
of free time and violence.</font>

15
00:01:07,730 --> 00:01:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was wandering around and some idiot 
picked a fight with me, that's all.</font>

16
00:01:11,770 --> 00:01:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then it was legitimate self-defense!</font>

17
00:01:13,570 --> 00:01:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's also...</font>

18
00:01:15,380 --> 00:01:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your face, I suppose.</font>

19
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The beautiful is nothing other than 
the origin of the fearsome."</font>

20
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:25,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, beautiful people 
are suited to torture.</font>

21
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:33,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

22
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can have this.</font>

23
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't say I'd do—</font>

24
00:01:36,790 --> 00:01:38,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a whip I used to use.</font>

25
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should be perfect to start with.</font>

26
00:01:47,550 --> 00:01:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very nice. It looks good on you.</font>

27
00:01:50,770 --> 00:01:52,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that reminds me.</font>

28
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:55,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never asked your name, did I?</font>

29
00:01:55,610 --> 00:01:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Hera.</font>

30
00:01:59,060 --> 00:01:59,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu.</font>

31
00:02:08,480 --> 00:02:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For your first time, 
that's very well done.</font>

32
00:02:11,970 --> 00:02:13,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How was it?</font>

33
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:15,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How was it? Exhausting.</font>

34
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a lackluster reaction. 
Isn't there anything else?</font>

35
00:02:21,620 --> 00:02:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dragging out the answers he had in him</font>

36
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with my own two hands 
felt... fun, I think.</font>

37
00:02:30,290 --> 00:02:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got a good sense for this. 
I knew you were suited for it.</font>

38
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! Now to contact the cleaner.</font>

39
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, hello?</font>

40
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It got messier than usual.</font>

41
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not me. A new guy.</font>

42
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care of it, will you?</font>

43
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's a weird guy.</i></font>

44
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for helping out again.</font>

45
00:02:54,940 --> 00:02:58,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Having clean torturers like 
you two around is a huge help.</font>

46
00:02:58,690 --> 00:03:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

47
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is the boy back there a new hire?</font>

48
00:03:02,310 --> 00:03:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

49
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's recently started working with me.</font>

50
00:03:05,590 --> 00:03:06,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

51
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:10,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were lucky to meet 
a good torturer like him.</font>

52
00:03:10,970 --> 00:03:13,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one who was lucky,</font>

53
00:03:13,070 --> 00:03:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">meeting a good, talented kid like him.</font>

54
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

55
00:03:22,910 --> 00:03:27,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That guy earlier mentioned 
"clean torturers." What does that mean?</font>

56
00:03:27,580 --> 00:03:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, in this business,</font>

57
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there are many torturers who'll torture 
people who aren't torture targets,</font>

58
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:35,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or who don't maintain 
proper confidentiality.</font>

59
00:03:35,900 --> 00:03:37,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's unbelievable, really.</font>

60
00:03:38,990 --> 00:03:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to produce results 
using honest methods.</font>

61
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:45,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Otherwise, no one will 
trust the kids of today</font>

62
00:03:45,230 --> 00:03:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who become torturers in the future.</font>

63
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? What's wrong?</font>

64
00:03:50,090 --> 00:03:53,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you start doing this work?</font>

65
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I tagged along with a torturer 
that I just happened to meet,</font>

66
00:03:57,370 --> 00:03:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the rest is history.</font>

67
00:03:59,260 --> 00:04:00,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it was just chance.</font>

68
00:04:06,540 --> 00:04:07,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

69
00:04:08,180 --> 00:04:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it suited me as a person.</font>

70
00:04:10,660 --> 00:04:15,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It felt like the truths I extracted 
filled the cracks I had in me.</font>

71
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one who dragged you into this,</font>

72
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but whether you continue or not</font>

73
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is for you to decide.</font>

74
00:04:31,030 --> 00:04:33,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Comfortable everyday life...</i></font>

75
00:04:33,930 --> 00:04:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I close my eyes, it's all wonderful.</i></font>

76
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I go with him...</i></font>

77
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:41,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll lose these kinds of days.</i></font>

78
00:04:44,690 --> 00:04:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who'd regret losing this everyday life?</i></font>

79
00:04:57,060 --> 00:04:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

80
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that bandage for?</font>

81
00:05:00,710 --> 00:05:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink.</font>

82
00:05:02,380 --> 00:05:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I quit school.</font>

83
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that was sudden.</font>

84
00:05:10,610 --> 00:05:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not gonna quit.</font>

85
00:05:13,270 --> 00:05:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dragged a young person 
with a promising future into this.</font>

86
00:05:16,110 --> 00:05:17,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take responsibility.</font>

87
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, of course. I'll do my very best.</font>

88
00:05:25,770 --> 00:05:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think? Do you feel 
like spilling what you know?</font>

89
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:30,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a stubborn one.</font>

90
00:05:32,020 --> 00:05:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry!</font>

91
00:05:33,530 --> 00:05:35,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My last job ran long.</font>

92
00:05:35,890 --> 00:05:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're late!</font>

93
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:42,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Von. He's in 
the same business as us.</font>

94
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you.</font>

95
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good work today.</font>

96
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:54,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for coming. It was a huge help.</font>

97
00:05:54,770 --> 00:05:56,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're quite welcome.</font>

98
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'll go and call the cleaner.</font>

99
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks!</font>

100
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-kun, was it?</font>

101
00:06:05,500 --> 00:06:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear you quit school.</font>

102
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:09,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

103
00:06:10,410 --> 00:06:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you've already realized this, 
but this is an odd industry.</font>

104
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:18,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't it be better to get back 
to a normal life as quick as you can?</font>

105
00:06:18,570 --> 00:06:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Normal is a pretty good thing, you know.</font>

106
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:25,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though, I guess since it was Hera-san
who caught you, it'd be hard to do.</font>

107
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened?</font>

108
00:06:29,610 --> 00:06:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He coughed up foam and collapsed!</font>

109
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

110
00:06:36,910 --> 00:06:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He isn't dead.</font>

111
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Izua.</font>

112
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there's a patient, 
of course I'll come.</font>

113
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:44,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so dependable!</font>

114
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:47,420
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Georgia"><font color="#212d3d">Ramen</font></font></b></font>

115
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:53,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you can see, I'm a doctor 
that these guys work to the bone.</font>

116
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A doctor?</font>

117
00:06:55,530 --> 00:07:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even the kind of trash that gets tortured 
needs medical treatment sometimes.</font>

118
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:04,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But when it's guys like that,</font>

119
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we're treating them when 
they're gonna get injured anyway...</font>

120
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:11,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not many doctors would do that willingly.</font>

121
00:07:11,050 --> 00:07:14,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I do it because 
I figure it's necessary.</font>

122
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do look after regular 
patients, too, though.</font>

123
00:07:18,410 --> 00:07:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you do this kind of work,</font>

124
00:07:20,170 --> 00:07:23,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you end up attracting 
all kinds of weirdos.</font>

125
00:07:23,860 --> 00:07:26,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like this guy, who seems unmotivated,</font>

126
00:07:26,050 --> 00:07:28,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but has a set of personal 
policies in his work.</font>

127
00:07:28,990 --> 00:07:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, yeah.</font>

128
00:07:30,710 --> 00:07:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or guys who appear detached and aimless, 
but are unexpectedly sensitive.</font>

129
00:07:35,460 --> 00:07:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because this work isn't easy.</font>

130
00:07:39,660 --> 00:07:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's also...</font>

131
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">punk kids with empty bellies...</font>

132
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:47,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and police officers 
who treat them to ramen.</font>

133
00:07:50,110 --> 00:07:51,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's all sorts of people here.</font>

134
00:07:52,690 --> 00:07:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

135
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given where I am now,</font>

136
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if I'd be able to help 
a kid who's like I was back then.</font>

137
00:07:59,470 --> 00:08:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you getting all sentimental?</font>

138
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:03,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want me to do a consult?</font>

139
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? It's not like that. 
It's just... you know.</font>

140
00:08:06,370 --> 00:08:07,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pull yourself together.</font>

141
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:12,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's give it our 
best tomorrow, too!</font>

142
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got myself a good 
partner now, after all.</font>

143
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:16,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

144
00:08:16,810 --> 00:08:19,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll try my best to live up 
to your expectations.</font>

145
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so dependable!</font>

146
00:08:31,570 --> 00:08:35,530
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#0c0b0e">3 Years Later</font></b></font>

147
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:35,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, this is the best!</font>

148
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san, thank you for 
doing this all the time.</font>

149
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you get sick of having 
omelet rice all the time, Noe?</font>

150
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope! Your omelet rice is just so good!</font>

151
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:48,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He seems like he'll make 
a good papa one day!</font>

152
00:08:48,430 --> 00:08:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As if.</font>

153
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'll go and check your job requests.</font>

154
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you would, please.</font>

155
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come back safely!</font>

156
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful out there today, too!</font>

157
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:08,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noe has grown up into 
a good boy, hasn't he?</font>

158
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has it already been three years?</font>

159
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

160
00:09:13,380 --> 00:09:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad Noe and I 
became family that day.</font>

161
00:09:18,900 --> 00:09:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to you and Noe, every day is fun.</font>

162
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Glad to hear it.</font>

163
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:27,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to stay like this forever.</font>

164
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, well...</font>

165
00:09:30,050 --> 00:09:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Von quit being a torturer...</font>

166
00:09:32,820 --> 00:09:36,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I'm sure people don't normally
last too long in this job, but...</font>

167
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:43,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu, do you think you'll be 
able to continue doing this?</font>

168
00:09:45,260 --> 00:09:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't imagine myself not 
being a torturer anymore.</font>

169
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably.</font>

170
00:09:51,330 --> 00:09:53,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do I put it? I feel like this job</font>

171
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has become the place where I belong.</font>

172
00:10:00,590 --> 00:10:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something I've been 
thinking for a while now.</font>

173
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be nice if I could create a place 
in this world where torturers could stay.</font>

174
00:10:11,530 --> 00:10:12,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A place...</font>

175
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:17,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hera!</font>

176
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn punks, running wild 
all over our turf like that...</font>

177
00:10:31,740 --> 00:10:33,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stupid brats!</font>

178
00:10:33,150 --> 00:10:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We won't let you off so easily next time.</font>

179
00:10:39,300 --> 00:10:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You understand now, don't you?</font>

180
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:44,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out of the torturing 
business while you can.</font>

181
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please...</font>

182
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please save him.</font>

183
00:11:08,930 --> 00:11:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

184
00:11:11,390 --> 00:11:15,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my fault someone so important 
to you is in that condition.</font>

185
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

186
00:11:31,690 --> 00:11:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my fault.</font>

187
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because Hera protected me.</font>

188
00:11:40,370 --> 00:11:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning... Siu.</font>

189
00:11:44,260 --> 00:11:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I seem... to have 
overslept... quite a bit.</font>

190
00:11:49,210 --> 00:11:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

191
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You moron.</font>

192
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow, ow, ow!</font>

193
00:12:00,890 --> 00:12:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

194
00:12:03,220 --> 00:12:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough of that.</font>

195
00:12:04,850 --> 00:12:06,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my responsibility, after all.</font>

196
00:12:08,130 --> 00:12:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides...</font>

197
00:12:11,230 --> 00:12:13,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the truth is, I've taken 
a bit of a liking to it.</font>

198
00:12:14,820 --> 00:12:18,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The old scar I've had 
since I was a child...</font>

199
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This new scar has swallowed it up.</font>

200
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:26,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's proof that I made these 
choices of my own free will.</font>

201
00:12:28,950 --> 00:12:32,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's why there's no 
need to make that face.</font>

202
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:34,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything is better this way.</font>

203
00:12:36,900 --> 00:12:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you stupid?</font>

204
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Siu, do you remember?</font>

205
00:12:42,770 --> 00:12:46,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was talking about wanting 
to make a place...</font>

206
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:51,950
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fefcfc"><font size="25">Contract Complete</font></font></font></b></font>

207
00:12:48,450 --> 00:12:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make it so that 
everyone can feel safer.</font>

208
00:12:51,950 --> 00:12:57,710
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fefcfc"><font size="7">Contract Complete</font></font></font></b></font>

209
00:12:52,730 --> 00:12:53,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just wait. Okay?</font>

210
00:13:04,970 --> 00:13:08,430
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="15">{\an7}Independent Torture Contractor</font></b></font></font>

211
00:13:04,970 --> 00:13:08,430
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="22">{\an7}Spirytus (Co.)</font></b></font></font>

212
00:13:13,620 --> 00:13:16,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem very comfortable 
with that appearance of yours now.</font>

213
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

214
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're beautiful once again today.</font>

215
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noe, you're such a good, honest boy!</font>

216
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:27,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noe, I finished up all 
the work allotted for today.</font>

217
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you've got anything else, send it over.</font>

218
00:13:28,740 --> 00:13:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I will!</font>

219
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san seems very eager 
to work, doesn't he?</font>

220
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hera-san, it's time 
to apply your medicine.</font>

221
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. So it is.</font>

222
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:43,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for always helping.</font>

223
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:45,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing.</font>

224
00:13:48,550 --> 00:13:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on!</font>

225
00:13:50,390 --> 00:13:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you! You have it all wrong!</font>

226
00:13:53,230 --> 00:13:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just a journalist!</font>

227
00:13:55,180 --> 00:13:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been made to pose as 
a torture target, that's all!</font>

228
00:13:58,250 --> 00:13:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Darn it...</font>

229
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:02,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, how did I get into this?</font>

230
00:14:02,730 --> 00:14:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why all the fuss?</font>

231
00:14:04,900 --> 00:14:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Untie me!</font>

232
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the truth! I'm telling you, 
I'm just a reporter!</font>

233
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you really a torture target?</font>

234
00:14:15,560 --> 00:14:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just said I'm not!</font>

235
00:14:18,690 --> 00:14:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry we treated you so roughly.</font>

236
00:14:23,330 --> 00:14:24,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should say you have!</font>

237
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm used to it.</font>

238
00:14:27,770 --> 00:14:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It happens a lot in my line of work.</font>

239
00:14:30,280 --> 00:14:34,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do hear a lot of information that would 
be inconvenient for various organizations.</font>

240
00:14:34,530 --> 00:14:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's why they sent you here, huh?</font>

241
00:14:37,290 --> 00:14:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly. They're merciless, you know?</font>

242
00:14:40,730 --> 00:14:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But never mind all that.</font>

243
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for earlier! 
You untied my ropes so quickly.</font>

244
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:47,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

245
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As thanks, if there's any info 
you need, just let me know!</font>

246
00:14:51,050 --> 00:14:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Despite how it looks, 
I'm good at what I do!</font>

247
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:57,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, this is my contact information.</font>

248
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Sowa. Looking forward 
to working with you!</font>

249
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:13,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! That reminds me...</font>

250
00:15:13,820 --> 00:15:17,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That girl from before, um...</font>

251
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sowa.</font>

252
00:15:18,160 --> 00:15:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's right.</font>

253
00:15:19,300 --> 00:15:21,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've asked her to do some 
simple digging for me.</font>

254
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

255
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was very cheerful, wasn't she?</font>

256
00:15:26,490 --> 00:15:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

257
00:15:27,380 --> 00:15:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just thought the two of you 
might get along surprisingly well!</font>

258
00:15:32,250 --> 00:15:33,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say...</font>

259
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">haven't you been smoking 
a little too much?</font>

260
00:15:36,380 --> 00:15:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should take a break 
every once in a while.</font>

261
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good to be passionate 
about your work, but...</font>

262
00:15:43,160 --> 00:15:44,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a pain.</font>

263
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello!</font>

264
00:15:48,510 --> 00:15:50,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're here again?</font>

265
00:15:50,900 --> 00:15:52,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! And I've brought provisions!</font>

266
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:54,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one asked you to.</font>

267
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, looks like this 
week will be rough, too.</font>

268
00:15:57,630 --> 00:15:59,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't look at that without permission!</font>

269
00:15:59,680 --> 00:16:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu, the color of your 
hair here is just like mine!</font>

270
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd you drop the honorifics?</font>

271
00:16:04,570 --> 00:16:07,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I <i>am</i> older than you, after all!</font>

272
00:16:08,340 --> 00:16:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop that.</font>

273
00:16:12,420 --> 00:16:13,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, look at that!</font>

274
00:16:15,330 --> 00:16:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's beautiful!</font>

275
00:16:18,550 --> 00:16:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This kind of thing is nice 
every once in a while.</font>

276
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:24,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad.</font>

277
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got to see you enjoying yourself.</font>

278
00:16:33,180 --> 00:16:34,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That scar.</font>

279
00:16:35,070 --> 00:16:37,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it exhausting 
covering it up all the time?</font>

280
00:16:38,500 --> 00:16:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if it is...</font>

281
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it was all my fault, so...</font>

282
00:16:45,690 --> 00:16:48,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to hide it 
from me, though.</font>

283
00:16:48,920 --> 00:16:52,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to know more about that scar...</font>

284
00:16:53,290 --> 00:16:54,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and about you.</font>

285
00:16:58,650 --> 00:17:02,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even though she didn't 
have anyone in this world,</i></font>

286
00:17:03,040 --> 00:17:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>she was ridiculously sunny and bright.</i></font>

287
00:17:05,540 --> 00:17:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She could find a way into 
people's hearts in a flash.</i></font>

288
00:17:09,980 --> 00:17:12,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That said, she knew 
loneliness all too well.</i></font>

289
00:17:12,970 --> 00:17:17,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When we were together, it felt like all 
the empty cracks inside me were filled.</i></font>

290
00:17:19,190 --> 00:17:21,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought it was the same for her.</i></font>

291
00:17:23,180 --> 00:17:29,150
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#0f0f0f">Thank you. 
Take care of yourself, okay?</font></font></b></font>

292
00:17:25,140 --> 00:17:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But she suddenly disappeared.</i></font>

293
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wondered vaguely if that 
was all there was to her.</i></font>

294
00:17:38,250 --> 00:17:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was reunited with 
her three years later...</i></font>

295
00:17:41,110 --> 00:17:42,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>in a hospital.</i></font>

296
00:17:46,010 --> 00:17:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why... are you in a place like this?</font>

297
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:51,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to contact you out of the blue!</font>

298
00:17:51,870 --> 00:17:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should apologize for
disappearing out of the blue.</font>

299
00:17:54,420 --> 00:17:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, you're right.</font>

300
00:17:56,360 --> 00:17:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mama! Who's that?</font>

301
00:17:59,730 --> 00:18:01,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's that?</font>

302
00:18:01,980 --> 00:18:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who could it be?</font>

303
00:18:04,490 --> 00:18:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are those my kids?</font>

304
00:18:05,930 --> 00:18:08,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. You can tell?</font>

305
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're adorable, 
aren't they? They're twins.</font>

306
00:18:12,110 --> 00:18:15,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this why you disappeared on me?</font>

307
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it is.</font>

308
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you couldn't depend on me?</font>

309
00:18:20,280 --> 00:18:21,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That wasn't it.</font>

310
00:18:22,690 --> 00:18:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just selfishly ran away. That's all.</font>

311
00:18:27,020 --> 00:18:28,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I thought that you</font>

312
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">might start to see me as a burden...</font>

313
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It terrified me.</font>

314
00:18:34,740 --> 00:18:38,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were the first connection I'd 
made that meant so much to me.</font>

315
00:18:45,710 --> 00:18:47,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a moron.</font>

316
00:18:47,270 --> 00:18:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, you're right.</font>

317
00:18:52,790 --> 00:18:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know...</font>

318
00:18:55,080 --> 00:18:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say... I only have 
half a year left to live.</font>

319
00:18:59,690 --> 00:19:00,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do they?</font>

320
00:19:04,900 --> 00:19:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sowa...</font>

321
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:08,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">want to get married?</font>

322
00:19:08,350 --> 00:19:12,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you always have this much compassion?</font>

323
00:19:14,020 --> 00:19:15,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would be better if we did.</font>

324
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:17,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After you're gone,</font>

325
00:19:17,840 --> 00:19:20,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you won't be able to look 
after them, right?</font>

326
00:19:20,270 --> 00:19:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

327
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that cold of me?</font>

328
00:19:24,330 --> 00:19:25,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

329
00:19:26,750 --> 00:19:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was that kindness of yours 
that I fell in love with.</font>

330
00:19:32,300 --> 00:19:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

331
00:19:39,250 --> 00:19:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over here! No, over here!</font>

332
00:19:41,080 --> 00:19:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you two. It's ready.</font>

333
00:19:43,370 --> 00:19:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

334
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa, it's amazing!</font>

335
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so good at this!</font>

336
00:19:47,970 --> 00:19:50,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and eat. The bus is coming.</font>

337
00:19:50,430 --> 00:19:51,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

338
00:19:52,420 --> 00:19:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The cats are so cute!</font>

339
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:57,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love omelet rice!</font>

340
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too!</font>

341
00:20:02,550 --> 00:20:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you quit smoking.</font>

342
00:20:05,670 --> 00:20:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every once in a while is fine.</font>

343
00:20:07,970 --> 00:20:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a little while since 
Sowa-chan passed away.</font>

344
00:20:10,990 --> 00:20:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are things after all that?</font>

345
00:20:13,230 --> 00:20:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Things are... not bad.</font>

346
00:20:15,630 --> 00:20:16,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

347
00:20:21,760 --> 00:20:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish Sowa had relied on me more.</font>

348
00:20:27,220 --> 00:20:29,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she did call you, didn't she?</font>

349
00:20:30,130 --> 00:20:33,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She entrusted her 
precious children to you.</font>

350
00:20:33,760 --> 00:20:38,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She definitely relied on you, 
and you're living up to it just fine.</font>

351
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of it... is what 
Sowa-chan chose for herself.</font>

352
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even this thing about my scars...</font>

353
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You took responsibility for 
them like no one else could.</font>

354
00:20:54,780 --> 00:20:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the best partner 
I could ever have.</font>

355
00:20:58,900 --> 00:21:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

356
00:21:00,450 --> 00:21:01,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, this is unusual.</font>

357
00:21:02,600 --> 00:21:05,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, you called out to me.</font>

358
00:21:07,530 --> 00:21:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've only been able to walk 
this far without losing my way</font>

359
00:21:10,760 --> 00:21:12,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">because you were there for me.</font>

360
00:21:17,250 --> 00:21:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one who should be thanking you.</font>

361
00:21:27,190 --> 00:21:30,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. When are we gonna get more workers?</font>

362
00:21:31,230 --> 00:21:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on. At least wash 
your face before you come in.</font>

363
00:21:35,590 --> 00:21:38,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just how many cases do you think 
I'm handling by myself here?</font>

364
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:40,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, now.</font>

365
00:21:40,090 --> 00:21:42,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have some new help coming tomorrow.</font>

366
00:21:42,620 --> 00:21:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, someone useless again, I bet.</font>

367
00:21:44,620 --> 00:21:47,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's rare for people 
to stick with this job.</font>

368
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many have we had quit this year?</font>

369
00:21:49,700 --> 00:21:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sixty-eight.</font>

370
00:21:52,360 --> 00:21:54,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of kid are you hoping for?</font>

371
00:21:54,010 --> 00:21:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoever comes, it's always the same.</font>

372
00:21:56,780 --> 00:21:59,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope someone you'll like shows up.</font>

373
00:22:00,210 --> 00:22:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

374
00:22:01,590 --> 00:22:04,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't get my hopes up.</font>

375
00:22:09,970 --> 00:22:14,270
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#010000">The <font color="#d9000d">Daily <font color="#269df2">L<font color="#171719">ife of a <font color="#ef670f">P<font color="#171719">art-Time <font color="#44c10c">T<font color="#171719">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

376
